## B2. `JToken` traversal
```
using Newtonsoft.Json;
using Newtonsoft.Json.Linq;

(...)

static IEnumerable&lt;JToken&gt; Traverse(JToken jo)
{
	if (!jo.Any()) yield return jo;
	foreach (var ch in jo)
		foreach (var x in Traverse(ch))
			yield return x;
}
