    }

**Clean up**

Don&#39;t forget to delete the pointer (Handle) that created by _MediaInfo_New_. You need to add:

    [DllImport(&quot;MediaInfo.dll&quot;)]
    private static extern void MediaInfo_Delete(IntPtr Handle);

